casebody.data:
In re A.R.R.

[Cite as In re A.R.R., 130 Ohio St.3d 261, 2011-Ohio-5346.]

(No. 2011-1027 Submitted September 20, 2011 Decided October 20, 2011.) O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, Lanzinger, Cupp, and McGee Brown, JJ., concur. O’Donnell, J., dissents.

{¶ 1} The discretionary appeal is accepted.

{¶ 2} The cause is remanded for application of State v. Williams, 129 Ohio St.3d 344, 2011-Ohio-3374, 952 N.E.2d 1108.

*262Michael M. Ater, Ross County Prosecuting Attorney, and Robert C. Hess, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. Timothy Young, Ohio Public Defender, and Amanda J. Powell, Assistant Public Defender, for appellant.
